<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>意大利阿博拉的一个小村庄里住着一个老木匠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的名字叫杰佩托。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一个人住在一个小屋子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他没有妻子，也没有孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每到夜晚降临，他就会觉得非常寂寞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天早上，他去森林里搜集雕刻用的木材。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个树枝和桌腿一样重。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是太短了，我不太满意。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个木材像大碗一样宽，但是不够深，我不太满意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这倒是一块好木材。但是太小了，我什么都做不了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托把木头扔到了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70141</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦！”一个声音说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70142</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？是谁在说话？有人吗？”杰佩托问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他非常困惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转过身，往森林的深处看，但是谁也没看到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一定是我的幻觉。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，他继续往前走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂！不要把我留在这里！我并不小！我是一块儿好木头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我是可以被充分利用起来的！”那个声音又说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托往回看，他吓呆了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那块木头会说话！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定是疯了！”杰佩托大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错，你是疯了！你把一块儿上好的木头丢在森林里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不对，我觉得自己疯了，因为我在跟一块木头说话！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂，我可是一块儿非常聪明的木头呢。”木头反驳道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，但是你只是一块木头！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只是一块儿木头？先生，把我带回家吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会让你知道，我不仅仅是一块儿木头而已。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托很担心自己疯了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他也很寂寞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个会说话的木头说不定会知道许多有趣的故事和笑话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他对自己说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他决定把这块木头带回家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我该用你做什么呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我可以把你雕刻成一根擀面杖，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>或者把你雕刻成一个鸟舍。”杰佩托说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188879</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？我可不想被雕刻。听上去太疼了！”木头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么如果我不把你雕刻成东西，你永远只能是一块木头。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。你可以把我雕刻成东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，请你一定要把我做成有趣的东西。”木头说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想做擀面杖。我也不喜欢鸟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想看看世界，到处去冒险。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那做成烟斗怎么样？富有的旅行家可以带着你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托提出他的建议。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要，我不喜欢烟。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我可以把你雕刻成象棋子。这样每天都是游戏！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他对自己的想法非常满意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，你根本就不明白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想跑。我想走。我想说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个小男孩儿怎么样？你可以把我做成一个小男孩儿吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260345</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小男孩儿？嗯……”杰佩托摸着鼻子想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“求求你了！我答应你，我一定做一个好男孩儿。”木头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你把我雕刻成一个小男孩儿，我就是你的儿子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们可以开开心心地住在一起！”木头补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其实木头根本就不想和杰佩托一起住。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它只想环游世界，到处冒险。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>木头这么说，只是希望杰佩托能够答应它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小男孩儿。好，我觉得这是个好主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们马上开始吧！”杰佩托露出了开心的笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他为自己将有一个儿子感到高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他为自己不再寂寞感到高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>